#: ../../source/contributing.rst:2
msgid "Contributing"
msgstr "贡献指南"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:4
msgid ""
"Thank you for your interest in contributing to Fabricatio! We welcome "
"contributions from the community. Please follow the steps below to get "
"started:"
msgstr "感谢您有兴趣为 Fabricatio 做出贡献！我们欢迎社区的贡献。请按照以下步骤开始："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:7
msgid "Design Philosophy"
msgstr "设计理念"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:9
msgid "Fabricatio follows an event-driven, capability-based architecture:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 遵循事件驱动、基于能力的架构："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:11
msgid ""
"**Composition over inheritance**: Mix capabilities (like ``UseLLM``, "
"``ProposeTask``) into Roles rather than deep class hierarchies"
msgstr "**组合优于继承**：将能力（如 ``UseLLM``、``ProposeTask``）混合到 Role 中，而非使用深层类继承体系"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:12
msgid ""
"**Python for ergonomics, Rust for performance**: User-facing APIs are "
"Python; performance-critical components (token counting, JSON parsing, "
"BibTeX management) are Rust"
msgstr "**Python 负责易用性，Rust 负责性能**：面向用户的 API 使用 Python；性能关键组件（token 计数、JSON 解析、BibTeX 管理）使用 Rust"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:13
msgid ""
"**Tasks carry state**: Tasks accumulate context as they flow through "
"workflows, enabling multi-step pipelines without global state"
msgstr "**任务携带状态**：任务在工作流流转过程中积累上下文，无需全局状态即可实现多步骤流水线"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:14
msgid ""
"**Cancellation-aware**: All async operations respect cancellation "
"signals, making Fabricatio suitable for interactive and long-running "
"agents"
msgstr "**支持取消**：所有异步操作都尊重取消信号，使 Fabricatio 适用于交互式和长时间运行的智能体"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:17
msgid "Getting Started"
msgstr "入门指南"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:19
msgid "**Fork** the repository on GitHub."
msgstr "在 GitHub 上**复刻**仓库。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:21
msgid "**Clone the Repository** to your local machine:"
msgstr "将仓库**克隆**到本地机器："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:28
msgid "**Install Dependencies**:"
msgstr "**安装依赖**："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:34
msgid "**Build the Package** in development mode:"
msgstr "以开发模式**构建包**："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:40
msgid "**Create** a new feature branch:"
msgstr "**创建** 新的功能分支："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:47
msgid "Optional: Generate Subpackages"
msgstr "可选：生成子包"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:49
msgid ""
"Generate a **Python** or **Rust** subpackage using the ``cookiecutter`` "
"template:"
msgstr "使用 ``cookiecutter`` 模板生成 **Python** 或 **Rust** 子包："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:51
msgid "For Rust:"
msgstr "对于 Rust："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:57
msgid "For Python:"
msgstr "对于 Python："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:63
msgid ""
"Templates: `Rust Template <https://github.com/Whth/fabricatio-maturin-"
"template>`_, `Python Template <https://github.com/Whth/fabricatio-"
"purepython-template>`_"
msgstr ""
"模板：`Rust 模板 <https://github.com/Whth/fabricatio-maturin-"
"template>`_，`Python 模板 <https://github.com/Whth/fabricatio-purepython-"
"template>`_"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:66
msgid "Testing and Quality"
msgstr "测试和质量"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:68
msgid "**Run Tests and Fix Linting Issues**:"
msgstr "**运行测试并修复代码格式问题**："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:76
msgid "Python vs Rust Contributions"
msgstr "Python 贡献与 Rust 贡献"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:78
msgid "Fabricatio is a hybrid Python/Rust project:"
msgstr "Fabricatio 是一个混合 Python/Rust 项目："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:80
msgid ""
"**Python packages** (``packages/``): User-facing APIs, workflows, "
"actions, capabilities. Use ``pdm`` or ``uv`` for dependency management."
msgstr "**Python 包** （``packages/``）：面向用户的 API、工作流、操作、能力。使用 ``pdm`` 或 ``uv`` 进行依赖管理。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:81
msgid ""
"**Rust crates** (``crates/``): Performance-critical components, exposed "
"to Python via PyO3. Use ``maturin`` for building."
msgstr "**Rust crate** （``crates/``）：性能关键组件，通过 PyO3 暴露给 Python。使用 ``maturin`` 进行构建。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:82
msgid ""
"**When to use Rust**: Token counting, JSON validation, BibTeX management,"
" file I/O helpers — anything where Python overhead matters at scale."
msgstr "**何时使用 Rust**：token 计数、JSON 校验、BibTeX 管理、文件 I/O 辅助工具——任何在规模下 Python 开销不可忽视的场景。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:83
msgid ""
"**When to use Python**: Workflow definitions, LLM integrations, action "
"implementations — anything user-facing or requiring rapid iteration."
msgstr "**何时使用 Python**：工作流定义、LLM 集成、操作实现——任何面向用户或需要快速迭代的场景。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:86
msgid "Submitting Changes"
msgstr "提交更改"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:88
msgid "**Commit** your changes with a clear and descriptive commit message:"
msgstr "使用清晰且描述性的提交信息**提交**您的更改："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:94
msgid "**Push** your feature branch to your forked repository:"
msgstr "将您的功能分支**推送**到您的复刻仓库："

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:100
msgid ""
"**Open a Pull Request (PR)** on the original repository's GitHub page. "
"Make sure your PR follows the project's contribution guidelines and "
"clearly explains the changes made."
msgstr "在原始仓库的 GitHub 页面上**发起拉取请求 (PR)**。请确保您的 PR 遵循项目的贡献准则，并清楚说明所做的更改。"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:103
msgid "Contribution Guidelines"
msgstr "贡献准则"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:105
msgid "Follow the existing code style and conventions (see :doc:`code-style`)"
msgstr "遵循现有的代码风格和约定（参见 :doc:`code-style`）"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:106
msgid "Write clear, descriptive commit messages using Conventional Commits format"
msgstr "使用 Conventional Commits 格式编写清晰、描述性的提交信息"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:107
msgid "Include tests for new functionality; test edge cases, not just happy paths"
msgstr "为新功能编写测试；测试边界情况，而非仅测试正常路径"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:108
msgid "Update documentation as needed — both docstrings and RST docs"
msgstr "根据需要更新文档——包括文档字符串和 RST 文档"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:109
msgid "Ensure all tests pass before submitting (run ``make tests``)"
msgstr "提交前确保所有测试通过（运行 ``make tests``）"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:110
msgid ""
"For Python contributions: type annotations required on all public "
"functions"
msgstr "对于 Python 贡献：所有公共函数必须添加类型注解"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:111
msgid ""
"For Rust contributions: all public items must be documented with ``///`` "
"comments"
msgstr "对于 Rust 贡献：所有公共项必须使用 ``///`` 注释编写文档"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:114
msgid "Review Process"
msgstr "评审流程"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:115
msgid "Open a PR with a clear description of what changed and why"
msgstr "提交 PR 时附上清晰的变更说明及原因"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:116
msgid "CI must pass (lint, type check, tests)"
msgstr "CI 必须通过（代码检查、类型检查、测试）"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:117
msgid "At least one maintainer review is required"
msgstr "至少需要一位维护者审核"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:118
msgid "Address all review comments before merge"
msgstr "合并前解决所有评审意见"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:119
msgid "Keep PRs focused: one concern per PR"
msgstr "保持 PR 聚焦：每个 PR 只关注一件事"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:121
msgid "We look forward to your contributions!"
msgstr "我们期待您的贡献！"

#: ../../source/contributing.rst:123
msgid "Happy coding 🚀"
msgstr "编码愉快 🚀"

